Java Programming by James Gosling [Available]

===== Library Menu =====
Enter your choice: 2
Enter book title to issue: 1984
Sourish issued: 1984

===== Library Menu =====
Enter your choice: 1

📚 Books in Library:
The Alchemist by Paulo Coelho [Available]
1984 by George Orwell [Issued]
Java Programming by James Gosling [Available]

===== Library Menu =====
Enter your choice: 3
Enter book title to return: 1984
Sourish returned: 1984
```

---

## 📖 Concepts Used

* Classes & Objects
* Encapsulation (private fields + getters/setters)
* ArrayList for book storage
* Basic input handling with `Scanner`



